DESCRIPTION: Complete implementation of a CronJob controller for Kubernetes using the Kubebuilder framework. The controller manages CronJob resources by scheduling and cleaning up jobs according to the defined reconciliation logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kubebuilder/blob/master/docs/book/src/cronjob-tutorial/controller-implementation.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
/*
