TITLE: Defining GroupVersion Info in Kubebuilder API
DESCRIPTION: Shows the groupversion_info.go file for a Kubebuilder API. This code defines the GroupVersion for the API and provides functions to add the types to the scheme. It's crucial for registering the API types with the Kubernetes API server.
