TITLE: Recording Kubebuilder Demo as Terminal Animation
DESCRIPTION: Comprehensive steps for creating a recorded demo of Kubebuilder, using asciinema to capture the terminal session and svg-term to convert it to an SVG animation. Includes setup, recording control, and post-processing instructions.
